{"tid":1471074,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【機場集會】機管局入稟申請禁制令　限示威者須在指定區域集會","createTime":"2019-08-14T07:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T07:54:06.000Z","uid":244704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ecfc9b1bc57f7d20284c9f8ff2b3362caa8c4855","tid":1471074,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:41:23.000Z","msg":"反對《逃犯條例》訂修的爭議不斷，示威者周一及周二發起「警察還眼」行動並聚集在機場，令逾幾百航班取消。機管區昨(13日)昨傍晚緊急向法庭申請禁制令，法庭昨亦在內庭內處理，機管局今早亦即「補飛」補交入稟文件。機管局今（14日）早透露已取得法庭臨時禁制令，根據機管局申請的文件，他們要求禁制阻礙機場的人士，進入離境大堂的指定位置，以及阻礙行車和行人通道。惟機管局非禁制所有示威，但需在入境大堂的指定位置。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3156688/org/db9c4e8e311825397e6f273084a5f4ab.jpg/tyi0GhxatuZwcsB-HopdG7hVlXNmyrd9yg0Z1MoNGdQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3156688%2Forg%2Fdb9c4e8e311825397e6f273084a5f4ab.jpg%2Ftyi0GhxatuZwcsB-HopdG7hVlXNmyrd9yg0Z1MoNGdQ&h=6281f5aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入稟狀內附的機場圖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3156691/org/f7a780241d5c2f92f5401e4f9528b714.jpg/waEwvpoG5DoZlX1jssZ2zRuVF69T9JCC9XCJJvVwiSY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3156691%2Forg%2Ff7a780241d5c2f92f5401e4f9528b714.jpg%2FwaEwvpoG5DoZlX1jssZ2zRuVF69T9JCC9XCJJvVwiSY&h=8fab24a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入稟狀內附的Plan II圖，圖內顯示於入境大堂的黃色「A」字格仔，是可供示威的地區。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3156690/org/c93aff6b9f12e08119ded7c80ee3e428.jpg/8BNSEvWqgmFd95eQNFmzNLqS7cI29smcb3p29G96dvQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3156690%2Forg%2Fc93aff6b9f12e08119ded7c80ee3e428.jpg%2F8BNSEvWqgmFd95eQNFmzNLqS7cI29smcb3p29G96dvQ&h=257f2a91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入稟狀內附的Plan III圖，圖內顯示於離境大堂的紅色區域，只限旅客及已允許的人士進入。<br />\n<br />\n原告機場管理局，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被告</span></span></span>任何非法阻礙及干擾機場的人士。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀設下示威範圍<br />\n<br />\n根據入稟狀的內容，除指定的地方外，機管局禁止被告參與在整個機場內的示威和抗議。而該指定的地方，只限於入境大堂的兩個區域(見圖：Plan II 黃色格仔)，但示威和抗議需和平和合法。此外，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">被告</span></strong></span>亦被禁止進入離境大堂的部份位置(見圖：Plan III 紅色位置)，除非是真正的旅客，或是以及獲得機管局和機場保安公司許可的人士。<br />\n<br />\n此外，機管局亦禁制<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>被告</strong></span></span>在機場內遊蕩，以及在機場或附近範圍阻礙行車和行人通道。機管局亦禁止<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>被告</strong></span></span>作出妨礙局方和機場保安公司的職員執行上述職務。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚內庭緊急處理<br />\n<br />\n根據入稟狀的資料，這入稟文件是於今早（14日）才傳入法庭，文件所見，代表律師亦包括資深大律師余若海。本報記者昨晚（13日）曾見由余帶領律師團隊，在晚上約9時半抵達高等法院，並在內庭內作緊急申請，余與律師團隊至晚上約11時才全部離開，但未有透露庭內內容。機管局至今早正式宣布已取得法庭禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCA1471/2019"},{"pid":"c67ed8fba7a303cf512607dad41f1932b6b02d19","tid":1471074,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:42:38.000Z","msg":"統一機場戰線，大家點睇？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469174</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【公投】大家覺得如果我號召班基督徒嚟機場攞住文宣圖sing hallelujah 有冇得諗？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470110\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470110</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[基督徒入] 求求你地入機場Sing Hallelujah<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469121</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"879e334b5a013bc566dd90a68fddcf67c9fb3e52","tid":1471074,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:45:02.000Z","msg":"只要無違反禁制令，都可以進入入境大堂。"},{"pid":"e9197709709ec0ae6d0284523e87c6a27e1501a6","tid":1471074,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:46:39.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"96ce85f6ee4ae8380461a24dfdb3e9cfee20fb9d","tid":1471074,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"ffe6ba5582ad8cec6602efe69d70806c08145492","tid":1471074,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:48:00.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"1e9f0d9e9055c1e81b4f48cc1d90a3be3c7c003f","tid":1471074,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:51:56.000Z","msg":"人多既話理鳩你咩"},{"pid":"12e735a79c1744a9a05494a3be0aa74a2f0c414f","tid":1471074,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:52:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推推推推推推推推推</span></span>"},{"pid":"be4219dc1173660a7fd151340c69adc02bef3a43","tid":1471074,"uid":38301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:54:06.000Z","msg":"1手<br />\n如果你已經喺機場<br />\n去巴士總站<br />\n搵個入口講得出2個鐘內嘅航班編號話接機就入到去<br />\n<br />\n唔好黑衫，唔好戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n航班編號自己check<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongairport.com/tc/flights/arrivals/passenger.page\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongairport.com%2Ftc%2Fflights%2Farrivals%2Fpassenger.page&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3XwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=b109468f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongairport.com/tc/flights/arrivals/passenger.page</a>"}]}